Subject: Work order {{workOrderNumber}} created
<h1>New work order</h1>
<p>{{t "greeting"}} {{recipientName}},</p>
<p>Work order <strong>{{workOrderNumber}}</strong> — “{{title}}” — has been created{{#if assetName}} for {{assetName}}{{/if}}.</p>
{{#if workOrderUrl}}<p style="margin: 20px 0;"><a class="btn" href="{{workOrderUrl}}">View work order</a></p>{{/if}}
